  "comments": "<p>Braille markings for the blind on front:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5fc0503e421ed.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5fc0503e421ed.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© gyoschak<br><br>UV activity:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a2c275992b8.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a2c275992b8.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© gyoschak</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a18bcdcffc.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a18bcdcffc.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Security thread:</p><p>Windowed into four sections on obverse side, inscription “BCCR 2000” when seen under backlight:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a1a4d6ad09.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a1a4d6ad09.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It has a multicolour tone and switches colours between blue and purple depending on which angle the note is held at.</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a1a6f28290.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a1a6f28290.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a1a7103b3e.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a1a7103b3e.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The map of Costa Rica in the top-centre-right of the obverse side is also printed in colour-shifting ink - switches colours between purple and magenta:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a1ae665492.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a1ae665492.jpg\"></a><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a1ae8485e8.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a1ae8485e8.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Blue iridescent stripe on reverse side - patterns:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/668a1b1bbecc2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/668a1b1bbecc2.jpg\"></a></p><p>© Kiet Tran</p>",
